project: Tips: Enemies are really dangereous and will start shooting upon seeing you. Jump on these demons to kill them.

Tips 1: Coins should be collected throughout the player's journey. Collect them. They will be useful later.

Tips 2: Hit bonusbox with player's head to discover hidden coin.
Tips : You have reach the end of level one. Go through the door to go to next level

Hello warrior!
I am Grimwald, the king's chancellor. This is where your journey begins. Our princess is kept in captive at Mephisto's house located   in "hell". Make your way to "hell" and save our beloved princess. 
Good luck on your journey

In a world where the king, the most powerful person on a cursed land, got his castle attacked and his daughter kidnapped by the demons sent by "Mephisto" also known as the "Dark Devil". 

The king is left with the sole solution to call for his strongest warrior, the Dark Knight, in the aim of bringing back the princess safe.
Tips: Watch out, moving ground ahead. Make sure you wait and get on them safely. Else you will die and have to restart the level.

Tips: Enter hidden level to collect additional coins and exit to continue on your journey
